{
    "version": 5,
    "bundle": "VGGYPGWVTSIE4GL3UFSSPRKL6Q5I3JKF",
    "type": "story",
    "storyId": "801049002",
    "title": "夕暮れの独り飯",
    "text": [
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "買い出しのため駅前を歩いていると、\r\n見慣れた制服が視界に入った。",
            "enText": "I was walking in front of the station \nto buy some groceries when I saw \na familiar uniform.",
            "nextBlock": 2,
            "origClipLength": 88,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 112,
                    "pathId": -3495822924251850602
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 99,
                    "pathId": 8899582596645922967
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 5469527506129000091,
            "blockIdx": 1
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ナカヤマフェスタ",
            "enName": "Nakayama Festa",
            "jpText": "……。",
            "enText": "…",
            "nextBlock": 3,
            "origClipLength": 68,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 102,
                    "pathId": -7318047631473182464
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 102,
                    "pathId": -4271742077521845442
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -6156090784793739566,
            "blockIdx": 2
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "彼女はなぜか寂れた路地へと入っていく。\r\n気になって追いかけてみると――",
            "enText": "She goes into a deserted alley for some \nreason. I was curious, so I went after her.",
            "nextBlock": 4,
            "origClipLength": 91,
            "pathId": 815356869182159512,
            "blockIdx": 3
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ナカヤマフェスタ",
            "enName": "Nakayama Festa",
            "jpText": "おい、コソコソつけ回して何のつもりだ？",
            "enText": "Hey, what are you doing sneaking around?",
            "nextBlock": 5,
            "origClipLength": 69,
            "pathId": 3838937784856337479,
            "blockIdx": 4
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ナカヤマフェスタ",
            "enName": "Nakayama Festa",
            "jpText": "返答次第じゃ……こっちも考えがあるが。",
            "enText": "Depending on the response… may \nhave some ideas for you.",
            "nextBlock": 6,
            "origClipLength": 69,
            "pathId": 7411534284462467880,
            "blockIdx": 5
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "後をつけた訳じゃなく、人の少ない場所へ\r\n向かうので心配になったのだと伝えた。",
            "enText": "I told her that I wasn't following her, but \nthat I was worried because she was going to \na less crowded place.",
            "nextBlock": 7,
            "origClipLength": 95,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 226,
                    "pathId": -3430002860538151538
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 166,
                    "pathId": -9206230637447792017
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -2084936528280969596,
            "blockIdx": 6
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ナカヤマフェスタ",
            "enName": "Nakayama Festa",
            "jpText": "ほう、担当でもないのに物好きなヤツだな。",
            "enText": "Well, you're not in charge, but you like it.",
            "nextBlock": 8,
            "origClipLength": 71,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 60,
                    "pathId": 4761035369352201765
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 82,
                    "pathId": -3570586853321698941
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -7057667818412062118,
            "blockIdx": 7
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ナカヤマフェスタ",
            "enName": "Nakayama Festa",
            "jpText": "心配しなくても、飯に行くだけさ。\r\n路地の奥に何件か行きつけがあってな。",
            "enText": "Don't worry, we're only going out \nfor dinner. I've got a couple of \nhaunts in the back alleys.",
            "nextBlock": 9,
            "origClipLength": 91,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 52,
                    "pathId": -2122517585171601741
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 102,
                    "pathId": -4540348254727407839
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -2944806231208033977,
            "blockIdx": 8
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ナカヤマフェスタ",
            "enName": "Nakayama Festa",
            "jpText": "小さい店ばかりだが、安くて美味い。",
            "enText": "They are all small, but cheap and tasty.",
            "nextBlock": 10,
            "origClipLength": 67,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 40,
                    "pathId": -7901370741601237216
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 78,
                    "pathId": -6229707684647105531
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -5037332440997892818,
            "blockIdx": 9
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ナカヤマフェスタ",
            "enName": "Nakayama Festa",
            "jpText": "だが少し迷ってるんだ。ホルモン煮込みと\r\nカレー、今日はどっちにするか……。",
            "enText": "But I'm a bit confused. Hormone stew or \ncurry, which to choose today…",
            "nextBlock": 11,
            "origClipLength": 94,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "ホルモン煮込みかな",
                    "enText": "Maybe stewed hormone.",
                    "nextBlock": 11
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "カツカレーがいいな",
                    "enText": "I like curry with pork.",
                    "nextBlock": 18
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 53,
                    "pathId": -2703802162619536953
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 105,
                    "pathId": 5535379758768850567
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 37360316361566387,
            "blockIdx": 10
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ナカヤマフェスタ",
            "enName": "Nakayama Festa",
            "jpText": "へぇ、ホルモン煮込み派か。珍しいな。",
            "enText": "So you're a hormone stew \nman. That's unusual.",
            "nextBlock": 12,
            "origClipLength": 68,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 57,
                    "pathId": -7391742192873735340
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 79,
                    "pathId": 5843164971010420771
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 3636328133429209997,
            "blockIdx": 11
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ナカヤマフェスタ",
            "enName": "Nakayama Festa",
            "jpText": "クセがあって苦手なヤツも多いが、\r\nなぜ選んだ？",
            "enText": "Many people don't like it, but \nwhy did you choose it?",
            "nextBlock": 13,
            "origClipLength": 76,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "コクがあって温まるから",
                    "enText": "Because it's rich and warming.",
                    "nextBlock": 13
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 65,
                    "pathId": -3692603554686703821
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 87,
                    "pathId": -8113976456929691570
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 2425956893924781155,
            "blockIdx": 12
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ナカヤマフェスタ",
            "enName": "Nakayama Festa",
            "jpText": "滋味を好むか……気が合うな。",
            "enText": "You like nourishment?… You're \nkindred spirits.",
            "nextBlock": 14,
            "origClipLength": 63,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 21,
                    "pathId": 4239887388704834027
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 74,
                    "pathId": -3647323115656668059
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 8740442283810130577,
            "blockIdx": 13
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ナカヤマフェスタ",
            "enName": "Nakayama Festa",
            "jpText": "学園で出る、今っぽい食いモンも\r\n悪くはないが――",
            "enText": "There's nothing wrong with a bit \nof modern school food, but…",
            "nextBlock": 15,
            "origClipLength": 77,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 66,
                    "pathId": -4225554326124221721
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 88,
                    "pathId": -5573456102325487958
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 4959465687723043302,
            "blockIdx": 14
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ナカヤマフェスタ",
            "enName": "Nakayama Festa",
            "jpText": "ただ茶色いだけの汁ににじんだ、モツの\r\n旨味と野菜の甘さに癒されたい日もある。",
            "enText": "There are days when you just want to soak up \nthe sweetness of the vegetables and the \nflavour of the motsu in the brown soup.",
            "nextBlock": 16,
            "origClipLength": 95,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 81,
                    "pathId": -2356542981376537790
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 106,
                    "pathId": 2793822441745226776
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -6220893857098998821,
            "blockIdx": 15
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ナカヤマフェスタ",
            "enName": "Nakayama Festa",
            "jpText": "……そういや、どこかのレース場にも、\r\n美味いホルモン煮込みを出す店があったな。",
            "enText": "… Well, there's a place at some racecourse \nthat serves a good hormone stew.",
            "nextBlock": 17,
            "origClipLength": 97,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 66,
                    "pathId": 634173484933665811
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 108,
                    "pathId": 1476919941808945778
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 1298374943598552817,
            "blockIdx": 16
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ナカヤマフェスタ",
            "enName": "Nakayama Festa",
            "jpText": "次は寄ってみるか……。まァいい。\r\nトレーナー、アンタは早く巣に戻んなよ。",
            "enText": "Next time you're in the area, stop \nby … Oh well. Trainer, you'd better \nget back to the nest.",
            "nextBlock": 27,
            "origClipLength": 93,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 56,
                    "pathId": 5953974164042683217
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 104,
                    "pathId": 4976547779352765923
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -9102590223457250841,
            "blockIdx": 17
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ナカヤマフェスタ",
            "enName": "Nakayama Festa",
            "jpText": "“カツ”カレーね……ゲン担ぎかい？",
            "enText": "\"Katsu\" curry… Are you trying to make money?",
            "nextBlock": 19,
            "origClipLength": 67,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 88,
                    "pathId": -6219443975458707056
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 78,
                    "pathId": 6014335185218890446
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -7687444457942083091,
            "blockIdx": 18
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ナカヤマフェスタ",
            "enName": "Nakayama Festa",
            "jpText": "担いだところで救う仏もいないだろうが。\r\n……それでも何かにすがりたくなるのが、\n業ってもんか。",
            "enText": "I'm sure there's no Buddha to save \nyou if you carry it… Still, it's \nthe karma that makes us want to hang \non to something, isn't it?",
            "nextBlock": 20,
            "origClipLength": 107,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 76,
                    "pathId": -4614160103923230395
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 118,
                    "pathId": 8274401560241372957
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 40768952098370927,
            "blockIdx": 19
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ナカヤマフェスタ",
            "enName": "Nakayama Festa",
            "jpText": "そうだな、今日はアンタにあやかるとしよう。",
            "enText": "Yes, I'm going to give you the \nbenefit of the doubt today.",
            "nextBlock": 21,
            "origClipLength": 72,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "学園にもカツカレーはあるけど",
                    "enText": "We have cutlet curry at the school.",
                    "nextBlock": 21
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 63,
                    "pathId": -1655527899240906861
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 83,
                    "pathId": -1656942993088738491
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -2299213848453049998,
            "blockIdx": 20
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ナカヤマフェスタ",
            "enName": "Nakayama Festa",
            "jpText": "あいにく、今日は独り飯の気分でね。",
            "enText": "Unfortunately, I'm in the \nmood to eat alone today.",
            "nextBlock": 22,
            "origClipLength": 67,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 53,
                    "pathId": 1888501416619457159
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 78,
                    "pathId": 2334421305320330138
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 4676172500394647192,
            "blockIdx": 21
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ナカヤマフェスタ",
            "enName": "Nakayama Festa",
            "jpText": "学園で食べると、アンタみたいなお節介が\r\nやたらと声をかけてくるんだ。",
            "enText": "When I eat at the school, meddlers like you \nare the ones who keep asking me for help.",
            "nextBlock": 23,
            "origClipLength": 90,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 48,
                    "pathId": 8306550699877523104
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 101,
                    "pathId": -4786449309742165907
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 2438232651257254835,
            "blockIdx": 22
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ナカヤマフェスタ",
            "enName": "Nakayama Festa",
            "jpText": "その点、裏路地の店なら\r\n注文の他は黙ってりゃいい。",
            "enText": "On the other hand, if you're in \na back alley, you can just order \nand keep your mouth shut.",
            "nextBlock": 24,
            "origClipLength": 78,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 39,
                    "pathId": 4644201738149970007
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 89,
                    "pathId": -7945165323441638775
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -2659040095549645267,
            "blockIdx": 23
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ナカヤマフェスタ",
            "enName": "Nakayama Festa",
            "jpText": "まァ、何も聞かず大盛りでよそってくる\r\n無言のお節介があったりもするが……。",
            "enText": "Well, there are times when I don't ask and \nthey just serve me a big bowl…",
            "nextBlock": 25,
            "origClipLength": 94,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 67,
                    "pathId": 490759483007154891
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 105,
                    "pathId": 8292166801612364368
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 6702072829591671183,
            "blockIdx": 24
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ナカヤマフェスタ",
            "enName": "Nakayama Festa",
            "jpText": "そういや、どこかのレース場にも\r\n大盛りで人気のカレー屋があったな。",
            "enText": "Well, there's a curry shop at \nsome racecourse that's popular \nfor its large portions.",
            "nextBlock": 26,
            "origClipLength": 89,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 48,
                    "pathId": -1671656570762277071
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 100,
                    "pathId": 6405670819627061746
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -8963961399455236534,
            "blockIdx": 25
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ナカヤマフェスタ",
            "enName": "Nakayama Festa",
            "jpText": "次は寄ってみるか……。まァいい。\r\nトレーナー、アンタは早く巣に戻んなよ。",
            "enText": "Next time you're in the area, stop \nby … Oh well. Trainer, you'd better \nget back to the nest.",
            "nextBlock": 27,
            "origClipLength": 93,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 54,
                    "pathId": 4655997109674951280
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 104,
                    "pathId": 8479123828355645254
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 6665515322946491801,
            "blockIdx": 26
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "そう言うと、ナカヤマフェスタは\r\n振り向きもせず、暗い路地へと紛れていった。",
            "enText": "Then, without looking back, Nakayama Festa \ndisappeared into a dark alley.",
            "nextBlock": -1,
            "origClipLength": 94,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 28,
                    "pathId": -8027593606778329450
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 28,
                    "pathId": 5523220661667662607
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -2729523696601800461,
            "blockIdx": 27
        }
    ],
    "modified": 1669946376
}